-- Google's Share of China's Internet Search Market Declines, iResearch Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-19T06:59:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/google-s-share-of-china-s-internet-search-market-declines-iresearch-says.html

          
          
             Google Inc. had 27.3 percent of
China’s Internet search-engine market in the second quarter,
falling from 29.5 percent in the previous quarter, research
company iResearch said in an e-mail today.  
 Baidu Inc.’s market share increased to 70.8 percent in the
second quarter from 67.8 percent, iResearch said.  
